        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer171444755" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10455802772026499838">So easy going - and then wham!<br/>Quentin Tarantino could learn a lot from E M Forster. He&apos;d learn that there&apos;s no need to pile on the menace in the early stages. The shock, when it comes is much more effective if the reader/viewer has been led into thinking all is ordinary and relatively safe. Forster is a master story teller, and a true philosopher as well.</span>
  <span id="freeText10455802772026499838" style="display:none">So easy going - and then wham!<br />Quentin Tarantino could learn a lot from E M Forster. He'd learn that there's no need to pile on the menace in the early stages. The shock, when it comes is much more effective if the reader/viewer has been led into thinking all is ordinary and relatively safe. Forster is a master story teller, and a true philosopher as well.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10455802772026499838" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

